Objective

Create a native iOS wrapper for the Photography Reference System that packages the existing generated HTML documentation into a standalone iPhone/iPad application.

The wrapper is a deployment target only.

It must never become the source of the documentation.

The HTML generated by build.py remains the single source of truth.

The implementation must also include an automated build and validation process so the wrapper can be regenerated and tested after every documentation build.

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Architecture

Photography Reference System

    YAML

       │

    build.py

       │

       ├── Website

       ├── PWA

       └── iOS Wrapper

The iOS wrapper consumes the generated Website output.

Never duplicate HTML.

Never manually copy files.

Everything should be automated.

