Acceptance Criteria

A successful implementation allows the following workflow:

python build.py build website

python build.py build ios

python test_ios_wrapper.py

Open Xcode.

Press Run.

The application launches showing the generated Canon R5 Reference.

No manual file copying.

No manual resource management.

No broken links.

No missing images.

No missing CSS.

No missing JavaScript.

All tests pass.
